org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql

Class QueryDisplay

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.QueryDisplay

  • public class QueryDisplay
extends Object
    Some limited query information to save for WebUI. The class is synchronized, as WebUI may access information about a running query.
